        <guid>https://lemoe.cn/blog/lemoe-cn-v3%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84-notion2hugo/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://lemoe.cn/blog/lemoe-cn-v3%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84-notion2hugo/header.png" alt="Featured image of post Lemoe.cn v3全新架构！Notion2Hugo" /&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;lemoe-v0&#34;&gt;Lemoe v0
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;最初的Lemoe只是一个静态站（当然可以请求Github API获取一些信息&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.lemoe.cn/#&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;bookmark&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/86a2785e-44d6-4687-b014-e69cdf5929e2/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T115938Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=1877232bded019ed424f87b26c65db3e0fa8c471accd4a5f1a83850e181d538d&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;lemoe-v1&#34;&gt;Lemoe v1
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;也许是对这个域名爱不释手，很快本站就使用WordPress搭建为博客站&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/c3192d1e-a70a-429c-ae02-55e737d35745/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T115938Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=94f43fa9e1ef31a76f1ddda739d47c819cceae6e42cda64f9ef8372fe68567a3&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用的&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/ShawnZeng1996/Memory&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/ShawnZeng1996/Memory&lt;/a&gt;主题&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WordPress是有个优秀的博客程序以及CMS，然而由于其历史包袱、运维以及安全性方面考量后，该方案最终停用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;lemoe-v2&#34;&gt;Lemoe v2
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/e2dfbdfa-8828-4f9d-957c-3aee966f3e80/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T115938Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=058610e92d80d62f411694314d1ef6c12af35045fdae5e6efce65292522919f7&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;V2站采用Hexo构建并使用了&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/YunYouJun/hexo-theme-yun&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/YunYouJun/hexo-theme-yun&lt;/a&gt;主题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;该版本通过Github+Vercel自动构建并部署上线，尽管不再更新，该历史版本仍可通过&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://legacy.lemoe.cn/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://legacy.lemoe.cn/&lt;/a&gt;访问。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;该版本在原有主题上定制，添加了jQuery-Pjax&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;同时，该站会在构建时生成版本信息（commit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/50f31740-5dcb-4738-985c-24e3fe4ced0f/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T115938Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=4c096e0d305779c2f663af0d2578d3376c541964ae2852f1cea9b5d16133507b&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;见&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/TennousuAthena/legacy.lemoe.cn/blob/master/get-version.py&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/TennousuAthena/legacy.lemoe.cn/blob/master/get-version.py&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不过由于维护本地Markdown文件并Push还是太麻烦（？），没有一种赛博的美。再加上与Pjax带来的兼容性问题遂放弃维护。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;lemoe-v3-当前版本&#34;&gt;Lemoe v3 ←当前版本
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;0wotop&#34;&gt;0wo.top
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;该实验站采用Nextjs在Vercel Edge构建&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;2c0b42e6-5aed-4973-9fcb-6a890032b084&#34; &gt;link_to_page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;效果很棒，可以99%展现Notion的形态，然而构建有延迟并存在构建失败产生404的问题，目前仍在测试。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;notion2hugo&#34;&gt;Notion2Hugo
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;当前版本会使用Notion API将某个Database的内容遍历并处理为Markdown文件。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;源代码见&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://git.qmcmc.cn/qctech/notion2hugo&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://git.qmcmc.cn/qctech/notion2hugo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;自动部署&#34;&gt;自动部署
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;项目采用Drone持续部署，使用n8n Notion Hook追踪Notion变化&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/eea605b8-b3a9-4d7a-a905-34d934736e7c/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T115938Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=9470296b4323f40496eb412d80e331a96c11314752e133ce28999dca4dab87a3&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最终在CloudFlare Pages上部署&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/2ad10ba5-f9d0-4429-9eed-7010ba798344/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T115938Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=2aa6fbb13734c1abe0dfd09f159b7f3db1daabeda071afe4b4d659c183696da4&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;lemoe-v31&#34;&gt;Lemoe v3.1
&lt;/h1&gt;</description>
